'''Decipher''' were the license holders and publishers of the [[Star Wars Customizable Card Game|''Star Wars'' Customizable Card Game]] between [[1995]] and [[2001]].

Decipher has been around since the 1980s through various board games. The motto for Decipher has been: "Decipher: The Art of Great Games."

